flowchart TD

A[Read Requirement]

A --> B[What is the user trying to achieve?]

B --> C[Write User Journey]

C --> D[What data is shown?]

D --> E[Where does data come from?]

E --> F[Design Screen Layout]

F --> G[Create Large Components]

G --> H[What state is needed?]

H --> I[Create Hook API]

I --> J[What external operations exist?]

J --> K[Implement Services]

K --> L[Connect Hook To Service]

L --> M[Connect UI To Hook]

M --> N[Test User Journey]

N --> O[Refactor Only If Needed]